p: The mean Cycle 1 DSNs observed with Rolontis in the current study were comparable or lower than what was demonstrated for pegfilgrastim. At the two higher doses of Rolontis studied, the mean Cycle 1 DSNs were statistically noninferior to pegfilgrastim, and the Cycle 1 DSN with the 270 μg/kg Rolontis dose was statistically superior to pegfilgrastim ( P = 0.023). In Cycles 2, 3, and 4, the DSN with 135 μg/kg Rolontis and 270 μg/kg Rolontis were noninferior to pegfilgrastim and the DSN with 45 μg/kg Rolontis was noninferior to pegfilgrastim in Cycles 2 and 3.
